comments: Murray (ATL) extends two hands to Beal's (WAS) body at the start of the drive and the contact affects Beal's SQBR.
Murray (ATL) rests his hand on Beal's (WAS) back as the players engage away from the ball and the contact is marginal.

Bey (ATL) moves alongside Wright's (WAS) path and marginal body contact occurs during his contest of the driving shot attempt. Bey lowers his arm down during the contest and marginal arm contact occurs after the release.
Capela (ATL) cleanly blocks the shot attempt prior to when the ball reaches its apex.
Bey (ATL) and Gafford (WAS) both go to the floor to secure the loose ball and marginal hand to hand contact occurs as Bey (ATL) dislodges the ball.
Beal (WAS) moves parallel alongside Young's (ATL) path to the basket and makes marginal side to side contact on the driving shot attempt.
Kuzma (WAS) cleanly blocks the shot attempt prior to when the ball reaches its apex.
Murray (ATL) briefly places and retracts his hand from Avdija's (WAS) right arm and the contact during the rebounding opportunity is marginal.
Gafford (WAS) legally contests Hunter's (ATL) perimeter jump shot attempt.
Murray (ATL) and Avdija (WAS) make simultaneous contact with the rebound, which is deflected upwards, and the arm contact following the deflection is considered incidental.
Avdija (WAS) lightly brushes Bey's (ATL) arm during the rebounding opportunity and the contact is marginal.
Bey (ATL) makes some contact to Avdija's (WAS) arm as both players are reaching for the loose ball.
Wright (WAS) maintains legal position in the court of play prior to coming into contact with the ball.
Hunter (ATL) makes hand on ball contact to dislodge the ball away from Wright (ATL).
Hunter (ATL) brings his hands toward Wright (WAS) and marginal contact occurs as Wright releases his pass.
Capela (ATL) lightly brushes Kuzma's (WAS) side and the contact during the layup attempt at the basket is marginal.
Bey (ATL) brings his forearm to Gafford's (WAS) back and initiates contact that dislodges Gafford during the rebounding opportunity.
Capela (ATL) establishes himself in Wright's (WAS) path and marginal contact occurs as Wright moves into the pick.
Young (ATL) jumps in front of Gafford (WAS) during the driving shot attempt and marginal contact occurs as Gafford goes into the air to contest the attempt.
Gafford (WAS) cleanly blocks the shot attempt prior to when the ball reaches its apex.
Hunter (ATL) moves toward Avdija's (WAS) space and marginal body contact occurs as Avdija releases his pass.
Murray (ATL) legally contests Beal's (WAS) jump shot attempt.
Murray (ATL) inbounds the ball within five seconds of receiving it from the game official.
Capela (ATL) holds his arms out slightly as he establishes himself in a screening position and marginal contact occurs with Wright (WAS).
Wright (WAS) legally contests Young's (ATL) perimeter shot attempt.
Murray (ATL) and Beal (WAS) engage and disengage as the screen is set and the contact is marginal.
Gafford (WAS) establishes himself in Murray's (ATL) path and does not deliver illegal contact when setting the screen.
Gafford (WAS) and Hunter (ATL) momentarily come together at the same spot on the floor and incidental foot to foot contact occurs.
Wright (WAS) firms up on his right leg and marginal contact occurs with Murray (ATL) as he fights over the pick.
Kuzma (WAS) establishes himself in Murray's (ATL) path and does not deliver illegal contact when setting the pick.
Young (ATL) extends and immediately retracts his forearm from Beal's (WAS) space and the contact is marginal.
Murray (ATL) jumps alongside Beal (WAS) during his step-through shot attempt and marginal contact occurs.
Goodwin (WAS) briefly places his hands on Murray's (ATL) sides during the inbound and the contact is marginal.

Capela (ATL) holds his arms out slightly as he establishes himself in Avdija's (WAS) path and marginal contact occurs during the screen. Beal (WAS) attempt to move around Avdija and trips on his teammates foot.
Beal (WAS) legally contests Young's (ATL) perimeter shot attempt.
Kuzma (WAS) legally contests Young's (ATL) perimeter shot attempt.
